<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; }
      .banner { background-color: #5B34EA; padding: 32px 0; text-align: center; }
      .banner-icon { font-size: 48px; }
      .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; color: #1D1A31; }
      .header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #5B34EA; margin: 0 0 24px 0; text-align: center; }
      .content { font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #777683; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .highlight-box { background: #F5F3FF; border-left: 4px solid #5B34EA; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .highlight-box p { margin: 0; color: #1D1A31; font-weight: 500; }
      .date-range { color: #5B34EA; font-weight: 600; }
      .button { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0; }
      .button a { background: #5B34EA; color: #FFFFFF !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
      .button a:hover { background: #4A2BC9; }
      .signature { margin-top: 32px; color: #777683; }
      .signature strong { color: #1D1A31; }
      .footer-container { text-align: center; width: 100%; margin-top: 40px; }
      #footer { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-icon">‚è∞</div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="header">Timesheet Reminder</h1>

      <p class="content">Hi <%= @name %>,</p>

      <p class="content">This is a friendly reminder to update your weekly timesheet for <strong><%= @company %></strong> on Miru.</p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p>Your logged hours from <span class="date-range"><%= @starting_date %></span> to <span class="date-range"><%= @ending_date %></span> are less than 40 hours.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="content">Please update your timesheet to ensure accurate time tracking and billing.</p>

      <div class="button">
        <%= link_to "Update Timesheet", root_url + "time-tracking", target: "_blank" %>
      </div>

      <div class="signature">
        <p class="content">Cheers,<br/><strong>Team Miru</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render "devise/shared/footer" %>
  </body>
</html>
